{"id":"P0001","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"village_dawn","bg":"bg_village_dawn","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"天亮之前，余火村的钟声响了三次。"}
{"id":"P0002","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"village_dawn","bg":"bg_village_dawn","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"第一次是为了叫醒还记得自己名字的人。"}
{"id":"P0003","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"village_dawn","bg":"bg_village_dawn","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"第二次是为了确认谁已经忘了回家的路。"}
{"id":"P0004","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"village_dawn","bg":"bg_village_dawn","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"第三次响起时，村外的麦田里站满了没有脸的魔物。"}
{"id":"P0005","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"home","bg":"bg_village_home","speaker":"母亲","portrait":"mother_warm","text":"艾尔，把汤喝了。"}
{"id":"P0006","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"home","bg":"bg_village_home","speaker":"母亲","portrait":"mother_warm","text":"你每次要逞强的时候，都会忘记吃东西。"}
{"id":"P0007","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"home","bg":"bg_village_home","speaker":"勇者","portrait":"hero_confused","text":"我没有忘。"}
{"id":"P0008","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"home","bg":"bg_village_home","speaker":"母亲","portrait":"mother_warm","text":"你看，你连勺子放在哪里都忘了。"}
{"id":"P0009","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"home","bg":"bg_village_home","speaker":"母亲","portrait":"mother_warm","text":"路上会很冷。记得这碗汤，不是因为它有多好喝，是因为有人希望你活着回来。"}
{"id":"P0010","type":"memory_offer","chapter":"prologue","scene":"home","bg":"bg_village_home","speaker":"系统","portrait":"system_memory","text":"发现初始记忆：母亲做的热汤。","memory_id":"mem_mothers_soup"}
{"id":"P0011","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"square","bg":"bg_village_square","speaker":"师父","portrait":"master_old","text":"拿着。"}
{"id":"P0012","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"square","bg":"bg_village_square","speaker":"勇者","portrait":"hero_default","text":"这把木剑不是我小时候用的吗？"}
{"id":"P0013","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"square","bg":"bg_village_square","speaker":"师父","portrait":"master_old","text":"是你第一次被我打哭时用的。"}
{"id":"P0014","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"square","bg":"bg_village_square","speaker":"师父","portrait":"master_old","text":"那天你哭得很丢人，但第二天还是来了。"}
{"id":"P0015","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"square","bg":"bg_village_square","speaker":"师父","portrait":"master_old","text":"别忘了这件事。剑法会变成本能，但教你拿剑的人不会。"}
{"id":"P0016","type":"memory_offer","chapter":"prologue","scene":"square","bg":"bg_village_square","speaker":"系统","portrait":"system_memory","text":"发现初始记忆：第一次拿起木剑。","memory_id":"mem_wooden_sword"}
{"id":"P0017","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"square","bg":"bg_village_square","speaker":"莉娅","portrait":"lia_sick","text":"艾尔，你真的要去魔王城吗？"}
{"id":"P0018","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"square","bg":"bg_village_square","speaker":"勇者","portrait":"hero_default","text":"如果魔王真的夺走了大家的记忆，总得有人去。"}
{"id":"P0019","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"square","bg":"bg_village_square","speaker":"莉娅","portrait":"lia_sick","text":"我昨天忘了父亲的脸。"}
{"id":"P0020","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"square","bg":"bg_village_square","speaker":"莉娅","portrait":"lia_sick","text":"今天早上，我差点忘了你的名字。"}
{"id":"P0021","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"square","bg":"bg_village_square","speaker":"莉娅","portrait":"lia_sick","text":"如果我真的忘了，你能不能替我记得？不是记得我可怜，是记得我曾经把这件事托付给你。"}
{"id":"P0022","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"square","bg":"bg_village_square","speaker":"勇者","portrait":"hero_resolved","text":"我会带着这句托付回来。"}
{"id":"P0023","type":"memory_offer","chapter":"prologue","scene":"square","bg":"bg_village_square","speaker":"系统","portrait":"system_memory","text":"发现初始核心记忆：出发的理由。","memory_id":"mem_reason_to_depart"}
{"id":"P0024","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"gate","bg":"bg_village_gate","speaker":"长老","portrait":"elder_gray","text":"这只背包只能装下有限的记忆。"}
{"id":"P0025","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"gate","bg":"bg_village_gate","speaker":"长老","portrait":"elder_gray","text":"越靠近魔王城，遗忘越重。想继续前进，就必须把一些记忆留在路上。"}
{"id":"P0026","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"gate","bg":"bg_village_gate","speaker":"勇者","portrait":"hero_confused","text":"如果我把重要的事忘了呢？"}
{"id":"P0027","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"gate","bg":"bg_village_gate","speaker":"长老","portrait":"elder_gray","text":"那你会走得更轻。"}
{"id":"P0028","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"gate","bg":"bg_village_gate","speaker":"长老","portrait":"elder_gray","text":"但你要明白，记忆不是只属于你的东西。有些记忆，是别人交到你手里的。"}
{"id":"P0029","type":"memory_offer","chapter":"prologue","scene":"gate","bg":"bg_village_gate","speaker":"系统","portrait":"system_memory","text":"发现初始核心记忆：我的名字。","memory_id":"mem_my_name"}
{"id":"P0030","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"gate","bg":"bg_village_gate","speaker":"母亲","portrait":"mother_warm","text":"艾尔。"}
{"id":"P0031","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"gate","bg":"bg_village_gate","speaker":"勇者","portrait":"hero_default","text":"我会回来。"}
{"id":"P0032","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"gate","bg":"bg_village_gate","speaker":"母亲","portrait":"mother_warm","text":"我不是让你一定回来。"}
{"id":"P0033","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"gate","bg":"bg_village_gate","speaker":"母亲","portrait":"mother_warm","text":"我是让你记得，曾经有人希望你回来。"}
{"id":"P0034","type":"choice","chapter":"prologue","scene":"gate","bg":"bg_village_gate","speaker":"系统","portrait":"system_choice","text":"初始背包容量为 4。请选择出发时保留的关系凭证。","options":[{"label":"标准开局：保留四段初始记忆","target":"P0035A","effects":{"gain":["mem_mothers_soup","mem_wooden_sword","mem_reason_to_depart","mem_my_name"]}},{"label":"轻装开局：丢下热汤，带上额外药草","target":"P0035B","effects":{"gain":["mem_wooden_sword","mem_reason_to_depart","mem_my_name"],"discard":["mem_mothers_soup"],"set_flags":["start_without_soup"]}}]}
{"id":"P0035A","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"gate","bg":"bg_village_gate","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"勇者把四段记忆放进背包，背包刚好合上。","condition":"has_memory:mem_mothers_soup"}
{"id":"P0035B","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"gate","bg":"bg_village_gate","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"勇者没有带走那碗汤的味道。屋里的炉火比刚才暗了一些。","condition":"discarded:mem_mothers_soup"}
{"id":"P0036","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"gate","bg":"bg_village_gate","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"勇者离开余火村时，太阳刚刚升起。"}
{"id":"P0037","type":"line","chapter":"prologue","scene":"gate","bg":"bg_village_gate","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"他的背包很轻。轻得像还不知道什么叫失去。"}
{"id":"F0001","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_path","bg":"bg_forest_path","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"遗忘森林里的树都长着相同的叶子。"}
{"id":"F0002","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_path","bg":"bg_forest_path","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"路牌上没有地名，只有被雨水泡开的空白。"}
{"id":"F0003","type":"battle","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_path","bg":"bg_forest_path","speaker":"系统","portrait":"system_memory","text":"自动战斗开始：空壳狼群。","enemy_id":"enemy_hollow_wolves","reward":["exp_small","gold_small","mem_fragment_forest"]}
{"id":"F0004","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_path","bg":"bg_forest_path","speaker":"迷路的孩子","portrait":"child_lost","text":"你见过一个村子吗？"}
{"id":"F0005","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_path","bg":"bg_forest_path","speaker":"勇者","portrait":"hero_default","text":"什么样的村子？"}
{"id":"F0006","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_path","bg":"bg_forest_path","speaker":"迷路的孩子","portrait":"child_lost","text":"我不知道。"}
{"id":"F0007","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_path","bg":"bg_forest_path","speaker":"迷路的孩子","portrait":"child_lost","text":"但我觉得那里有人在等我。"}
{"id":"F0008","type":"memory_offer","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_path","bg":"bg_forest_path","speaker":"系统","portrait":"system_memory","text":"发现记忆：有人等我。","memory_id":"mem_someone_waits"}
{"id":"F0009","type":"memory_offer","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_path","bg":"bg_forest_path","speaker":"系统","portrait":"system_memory","text":"发现记忆：被抛下的下午。","memory_id":"mem_abandoned_afternoon"}
{"id":"F0010","type":"choice","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_path","bg":"bg_forest_path","speaker":"系统","portrait":"system_choice","text":"选择拾取哪段记忆。若背包已满，将进入替换界面。","options":[{"label":"拾取：有人等我（承认仍有人在路的另一端）","target":"F0011A","effects":{"gain":["mem_someone_waits"],"open_memory_replace":true}},{"label":"拾取：被抛下的下午（学会一个人也能走）","target":"F0011B","effects":{"gain":["mem_abandoned_afternoon"],"open_memory_replace":true}},{"label":"都不拾取","target":"F0011C","effects":{}}]}
{"id":"F0011A","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_path","bg":"bg_forest_path","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"勇者把那句“有人等我”放进背包，森林深处亮起一小点营火。","condition":"has_memory:mem_someone_waits"}
{"id":"F0011B","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_path","bg":"bg_forest_path","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"勇者把那个被抛下的下午放进背包，身后的脚步声变少了。","condition":"has_memory:mem_abandoned_afternoon"}
{"id":"F0011C","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_path","bg":"bg_forest_path","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"勇者没有拾起新的记忆，迷路的孩子很快忘了自己刚才说过话。"}
{"id":"F0012","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_camp","bg":"bg_forest_camp","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"夜里，营火像一只快要闭上的眼睛。"}
{"id":"F0013","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_camp","bg":"bg_forest_camp","speaker":"营火旁的人影","portrait":"camp_shadow","text":"你也在赶路吗？","condition":"has_memory:mem_someone_waits"}
{"id":"F0014","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_camp","bg":"bg_forest_camp","speaker":"勇者","portrait":"hero_confused","text":"你是谁？","condition":"has_memory:mem_someone_waits"}
{"id":"F0015","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_camp","bg":"bg_forest_camp","speaker":"营火旁的人影","portrait":"camp_shadow","text":"我不知道。我只记得应该等一个人。","condition":"has_memory:mem_someone_waits"}
{"id":"F0016","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_camp","bg":"bg_forest_camp","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"营火没有变暖。勇者吃下干硬的面包，很快继续上路。","condition":"not_has_memory:mem_someone_waits"}
{"id":"F0017","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_camp","bg":"bg_forest_camp","speaker":"迷路的孩子","portrait":"child_lost","text":"他们以前就是人。忘了名字，忘了家，忘了为什么害怕。最后只剩下饥饿。"}
{"id":"F0018","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_camp","bg":"bg_forest_camp","speaker":"勇者","portrait":"hero_hurt","text":"那杀死他们算什么？"}
{"id":"F0019","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_camp","bg":"bg_forest_camp","speaker":"迷路的孩子","portrait":"child_lost","text":"也许是帮他们结束。也许只是你走得更远的办法。"}
{"id":"F0020","type":"memory_offer","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_camp","bg":"bg_forest_camp","speaker":"系统","portrait":"system_memory","text":"发现记忆：不再解释。","memory_id":"mem_no_more_explaining"}
{"id":"F0021","type":"choice","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_camp","bg":"bg_forest_camp","speaker":"系统","portrait":"system_choice","text":"是否拾取“不再解释”？","options":[{"label":"拾取：不再解释","target":"F0022A","effects":{"gain":["mem_no_more_explaining"],"open_memory_replace":true}},{"label":"不拾取","target":"F0022B","effects":{}}]}
{"id":"F0022A","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_camp","bg":"bg_forest_camp","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"勇者把解释的话咽回去。剑鞘轻了一点。","condition":"has_memory:mem_no_more_explaining"}
{"id":"F0022B","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_camp","bg":"bg_forest_camp","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"勇者没有拾起那段沉默。他仍然觉得，总有些话应该说出口。"}
{"id":"F0023","type":"battle","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_deep","bg":"bg_forest_deep","speaker":"系统","portrait":"system_memory","text":"自动战斗开始：无名鹿、空壳巡林人。","enemy_id":"enemy_nameless_deer,enemy_hollow_warden","reward":["exp_mid","gold_mid","mem_fragment_forest"]}
{"id":"F0024","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_old_shrine","bg":"bg_forest_old_shrine","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"森林深处有一座小祠堂，供桌上摆着一只空碗。碗沿很旧，像被很多人端起过。"}
{"id":"F0025","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_old_shrine","bg":"bg_forest_old_shrine","speaker":"勇者","portrait":"hero_hurt","text":"这味道……像家里的汤。有人把碗推到我面前，说路上会冷。","condition":"has_memory:mem_mothers_soup"}
{"id":"F0026","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_old_shrine","bg":"bg_forest_old_shrine","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"勇者看着空碗。它只是一只空碗，既不温暖，也不通向任何一间屋子。","condition":"discarded:mem_mothers_soup"}
{"id":"F0027","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_old_shrine","bg":"bg_forest_old_shrine","speaker":"记忆中的莉娅","portrait":"memory_lia","text":"如果我忘了，你能替我记得吗？这是我交给你的，不是命令。","condition":"has_memory:mem_reason_to_depart"}
{"id":"F0028","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_old_shrine","bg":"bg_forest_old_shrine","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"空碗旁边刻着一句话：要替谁记得？字还在，问题也还在，但它没有指向任何人。","condition":"discarded:mem_reason_to_depart"}
{"id":"F0029","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_boss","bg":"bg_forest_boss","speaker":"忘名猎人","portrait":"hunter_hollow","text":"站住。告诉我，你叫什么？"}
{"id":"F0030","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_boss","bg":"bg_forest_boss","speaker":"勇者","portrait":"hero_default","text":"我叫艾尔。","condition":"has_memory:mem_my_name"}
{"id":"F0031","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_boss","bg":"bg_forest_boss","speaker":"勇者","portrait":"hero_confused","text":"我是……去魔王城的人。","condition":"not_has_memory:mem_my_name"}
{"id":"F0032","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_boss","bg":"bg_forest_boss","speaker":"忘名猎人","portrait":"hunter_hollow","text":"那不是名字。我以前也有名字。我的女儿每天在门口喊它。"}
{"id":"F0033","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_boss","bg":"bg_forest_boss","speaker":"忘名猎人","portrait":"hunter_hollow","text":"后来她忘了怎么喊，我就把自己挂在这片森林里。"}
{"id":"F0034","type":"choice","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_boss","bg":"bg_forest_boss","speaker":"系统","portrait":"system_choice","text":"忘名猎人要求你献出名字。名字不是力量，但它是世界呼唤你的方式。","options":[{"label":"拒绝，保留名字","requires":"has_memory:mem_my_name","target":"F0035A","effects":{}},{"label":"献出名字，让猎人想起一点东西","requires":"has_memory:mem_my_name","target":"F0035B","effects":{"discard":["mem_my_name"],"gain":["mem_empty_nameplate"],"set_flags":["gave_name_to_hunter","ui_name_erased"]}},{"label":"沉默，准备战斗","target":"F0035C","effects":{}}]}
{"id":"F0035A","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_boss","bg":"bg_forest_boss","speaker":"勇者","portrait":"hero_resolved","text":"这是我的名字。不能给你。","condition":"has_memory:mem_my_name"}
{"id":"F0035B","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_boss","bg":"bg_forest_boss","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"勇者把名字递出去。猎人的弓弦松了一瞬，像终于听见远处有人喊他回家。","condition":"has_flag:gave_name_to_hunter"}
{"id":"F0035C","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_boss","bg":"bg_forest_boss","speaker":"勇者","portrait":"hero_default","text":"让开。"}
{"id":"F0036","type":"battle","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_boss","bg":"bg_forest_boss","speaker":"系统","portrait":"system_memory","text":"Boss 战开始：忘名猎人。","enemy_id":"boss_nameless_hunter","reward":["chapter_unlock_mountain"]}
{"id":"F0037","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_boss","bg":"bg_forest_boss","speaker":"忘名猎人","portrait":"hunter_human","text":"我想起来一点了。她不是在门口喊一个称号。她是在喊我。"}
{"id":"F0038","type":"memory_gain","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_boss","bg":"bg_forest_boss","speaker":"系统","portrait":"system_memory","text":"获得记忆：空名牌。它不是你的名字，只是一块曾经属于某个人的空白。","condition":"not_has_memory:mem_empty_nameplate","effects":{"gain":["mem_empty_nameplate"],"open_memory_replace":true}}
{"id":"F0039","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_boss","bg":"bg_forest_boss","speaker":"系统","portrait":"system_memory","text":"空名牌上的裂痕变深了。它帮猎人想起一点声音，也让勇者少了一种被呼唤的方式。","condition":"has_memory:mem_empty_nameplate"}
{"id":"F0040","type":"line","chapter":"forest","scene":"forest_path","bg":"bg_forest_path","speaker":"旁白","portrait":"none","text":"穿过森林后，勇者发现背包比出发时更重。不是因为装进了更多东西，而是因为他开始知道每一格都连着某个人、某句话、某个仍在等待回应的地方。"}
